2 February 2014Members of the media are advised that there will be a Cabinet Lekgotla starting from the 4th to the 6th of February 2014 at the Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria. A photo opportunity of all members of Cabinet and brief remarks by Minister Collins Chabane is scheduled to take place as follows:Date: Tuesday, 4th February 2014 Time: 10h00 Venue: Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria (access through Gate 10)All media interested to cover this session are requested to forward their details using the table below to ireen@gcis.gov.za or Pheliswa@gcis.gov.za .NB: RSVP is strictly essential. The deadline is Monday, 3rd February 2014. Only media with either a Press Card, ID or Passport will be allowed access.Name &amp; surname: Organisation ID/Passport no: Car registration Contact no:Enquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139Issued by: Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)